<figureCitation box="[1346,1427,942,966]" captionStart="FIGURES 46 – 54" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1376,1399]" captionTargetBox="[152,1431,181,1364]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,175,1367]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 46 – 54. Ovipositor and forewing. 46 – 47: T. fasciatus Li &amp; Wang, second valvulae and apex of second valvulae respectively, lateral view; 48 – 49: first valvulae and apex of first valvulae respectively, laterior view; 50: T. bannaensis sp. n.; 51: T. fasciatus Li &amp; Wang; 52: T. flavifrons (Matsumura) comb. n.; 53: T. quadragulatus sp. n.; 54: T. luchunensis sp. n." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/199899/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="45">
